{"type":null,"faqId":31855,"title":"如何使用 WLAN 热点共享数据网络？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>支持数据业务的手机可以作为 WLAN 热点。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如需使用 WLAN 热点功能，请先开启手机的数据开关。其他设备通过手机共享的网络上网时，将使用手机中 SIM 卡的数据流量。您可以参考如下步骤进行设置：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕上点击“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在“无线和网络”区域，点击“更多... &gt; 移动网络共享 &gt; 便携式 WLAN 热点”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98969\" style=\"width:5.164583in;height:2.4430556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击或滑动热点名称后的开关至 “</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98970\" style=\"width:0.28541666in;height:0.20625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，开启便携式 WLAN 热点。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-2</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98971\" style=\"width:2.6840277in;height:3.948611in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击“配置 WLAN 热点”，然后根据界面显示配置您的无线局域网网络名称、密码等信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-3</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98972\" style=\"width:5.165278in;height:3.7041667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>配置完成后，其他需要上网的无线设备可以搜索并连接至手机提供的 WLAN 热点。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98973\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6375","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1435287939000,"seriesProductName":"DAV-703L","visitedTimes":72,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"wifi 热点,热点,共享网络,网络共享","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}